Package gov.nih.nci.hl7.csv

All CSV related functionality.

          Description

Interface Summary
CSVMetaGeneratorUtil An interface that allows csv metadata to be autogenerated from disparate data sources.
 

Class Summary
CSVDataResult Contains CSV data information and validation results.
CSVMetaBuilder Builds a csv specification from a csv meta object graph.
CSVMetaFromInstanceUtil Generates a "starting point" csv meta object graph from a CSV instance.
CSVMetaLookup Provides quick access when doing csv metadata lookups.
CSVMetaParserImpl Builds a csv meta object graph from a csv specification.
CSVMetaReportGenerator Generates a SCM report (in Excel format).
CSVMetaResult Contains CSV meta information and validation results.
SegmentedCSVParserImpl Parses csv datafiles that are based on a certain csv meta specification.
